{"tid":805512,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去旅行要去盡到極致","createTime":"2018-09-04T01:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T03:42:59.000Z","uid":183708,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"016ea6413d8b8fb63052cce824a58ea656d4cd60","tid":805512,"uid":183708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"香港人中意去旅行已經街知巷聞<br />\n<br />\n但係近排日本天災頻頻，水災，又打風，地震，居然少少危機意識都無<br />\n<br />\n前晚食飯，其中一個朋友今日出發班機取消咗，因為打風無法起飛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全枱人的反應居然係去咗先，到咗先算<br />\n<br />\n面對災禍，全部人的反應係買咗保險未<br />\n<br />\n平日唔肯捱眼瞓嘅朋友，居然肯坐凌晨機瞓機場"},{"pid":"0c562d66d85827a6b60973441bcd6d4c21da7c3c","tid":805512,"uid":143443,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"因為香港令人窒息到就算客死他鄉都唔想留係度"},{"pid":"d9bf021e1efc6581ff6d813dd8b8516f533b6376","tid":805512,"uid":50502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"恐襲都照去啦 打風落雨算d 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168573f49643a702fd54af2327e04ea91eb24c7c","tid":805512,"uid":77461,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"行程可以改 無叫你去高危地方<br />\n你講到日本遇天災 會一去不返<br />\n <br />\n有得揀 一定飛咗先 情願訓酒店 食樓下7仔<br />\n反正都請咗假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11dc7bb8fa99da8b7eb28a6218add5187b0ed635","tid":805512,"uid":183708,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"0c562d66d85827a6b60973441bcd6d4c21da7c3c","tid":805512,"uid":143443,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"因為香港令人窒息到就算客死他鄉都唔想留係度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"因為咁，所以邊個唔好彩就要其他人一齊夾錢埋單包機?"},{"pid":"3c57434fa7b99f6d3fad6d42b9b2fd0c1f5449cb","tid":805512,"uid":183708,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"168573f49643a702fd54af2327e04ea